Smart Productivity & Health Monitoring System

An AI-powered real-time productivity and wellness monitoring system built using Python, OpenCV, and MediaPipe. The system tracks posture, eye fatigue, blink rate, productivity, and screen usage through live webcam analysis while generating analytics reports and health insights.

Features

Real-time webcam monitoring
Posture detection and correction alerts
Eye fatigue and blink tracking
Smart break reminders
Productivity and focus tracking
Screen-time monitoring
CSV data logging
Automated daily analytics reports
Interactive dashboard and visual graphs
Productivity vs distraction insights
Water and stretch reminders
Tech Stack

Python
OpenCV
MediaPipe
NumPy
Pandas
Matplotlib
Tkinter
